metadata.description:
This is the first NFT that provides ownership rights for a legal entity that owns a property. The property subject to the ownership rights is located at 41 Verkhovinnaya street, Kyiv, Ukraine (registration number of immovable property object: 690571680000).

The owner of the NFT becomes an owner of the property only if a real name and ID information are provided at https://propy.com/nft and terms and conditions are accepted.

Propy administers the process and operations of this NFT.
metadata.name: PropyNFT
